                        <content>
                           <table class="TBL">
                              <tr>
                                 <td>
                                    <p>Spain</p>
                                 </td>
                                 <td>
                                    <p>6000 tonnes</p>
                                 </td>
                              </tr>
                           </table>
                        </content>
                     </alinea>
                     <alinea>
                        <content>
                           <p>Within this category, a maximum of six vessels may be deployed in Mauritanian waters at any one time;</p>
                        </content>
                     </alinea>
                  </point>
                  <point>
                     <num>(c)</num>
                     <alinea>
                        <content>
                           <p>category 3 &#45; Vessels fishing for demersal species other than black hake with gear other than trawls:</p>
                        </content>
                     </alinea>
                     <alinea>
                        <content>
                           <table class="TBL">
                              <tr>
                                 <td>
