                              </tr>
                           </table>
                        </content>
                     </alinea>
                     <alinea>
                        <content>
                           <p>During the period of application of the extension of the Protocol, the following number of quarterly licences shall be held by Member States:</p>
                        </content>
                     </alinea>
                     <alinea>
