                              </tr>
                           </table>
                        </content>
                     </alinea>
                     <alinea>
                        <content>
                           <p>Member States shall inform the Commission if certain licences may be placed at the disposal of other Member States.</p>
                        </content>
                     </alinea>
                     <alinea>
                        <content>
                           <p>Within this category, a maximum of 19 vessels may be deployed in Mauritanian waters at any one time;</p>
                        </content>
                     </alinea>
                  </point>
                  <point>
                     <num>(g)</num>
                     <alinea>
                        <content>
                           <p>category 7 &#45; Non-freezer pelagic vessels:</p>
                        </content>
                     </alinea>
                     <alinea>
                        <content>
                           <table class="TBL">
                              <tr>
                                 <td>
                                    <p>Ireland</p>
                                 </td>
                                 <td>
                                    <p>15000 tonnes</p>
                                 </td>
                              </tr>
                           </table>
                        </content>
                     </alinea>
                     <alinea>
                        <content>
                           <p>If not used, these fishing opportunities shall be transferred to category 6 according to the method of allocation of that category;</p>
                        </content>
                     </alinea>
                  </point>
                  <point>
                     <num>(h)</num>
                     <alinea>
                        <content>
                           <p>category 2a &#45; Black hake (freezer) trawlers:</p>
                        </content>
                     </alinea>
                     <alinea>
                        <content>
